<date month='September' day='23' year='2016' />

<abstract><t>The BGP Communities Attribute [RFC1997] is heavily used by operators, but is inadequate to represent large enough values, particularly Four-octet Autonomous System numbers [RFC6793] plus additional values.  This document describes an extension to BGP [RFC4271] to address this need with a new extended form of the BGP community Attribute.</t></abstract>

